OL,11,Fand Nigel Bateson (cameraman) is
OL,12,Fawarded MBE;
OL,13,
OL,14,F- for ITN, Michael Nicholson (foreign
OL,15,Fcorrespondent) is awarded OBE and
OL,16,FEugene Campbell (cameraman) is awarded
OL,17,FMBE.
